**Short Description:**

This lab demonstrates **Prompt Engineering and Conversation Memory using LangChain and Hugging Face models**. 
A **FLAN-T5 language model** is used to generate responses to user questions. 
The lab shows how prompts work with and without memory and how conversation history can be stored to maintain context in AI interactions.
It helps understand how **LLMs handle prompts and maintain conversation flow in chat-based AI systems**.

